high_descs: Turn and go to the trashcan by the sink.
Pick up a bar of soap in the trashcan.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Wash the bar of soap in the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move a washed bar of soap to the dresser.

high_descs: Go forward to the garbage can that is between the sink and cabinet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the garbage can.
Turn around, head to the right, hang a right past the sink, face the sink.
Put the soap in the sink, turn the water on to rinse if off, then pick it back up.
Turn to the right, go to the wall, hang a left, go forward, then hang a left and go to the cabinet right of the garbage can.
Put the soap in the bottom drawer of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put clean soap in a drawer.

high_descs: walk to face a grey garbage can to the right of the sink
pick up the pick soap bar from the garbage can
walk to face the left side of the sink
wash the soap in the sink, pick up the soap bar from the sink
walk to face the bureau to the right of the grey garbage can
put the soap in the bottom drawer of the bureau
anns.task_desc: put a washed bar of soap in a bureau drawer
